1. Ona je *slobodna* osoba. (She is a free person.)
2. On je bio *slobodan* da odabere svoj put. (He was free to choose his own path.)
3. *Slobodno* vrijeme je najbolji dio dana. (Free time is the best part of the day.)
4. *Slobodna* volja je najveća vrijednost. (Free will is the greatest value.)
5. *Slobodni* građani se bore za svoje pravo. (Free citizens fight for their right.)
6. Nisam *slobodan* da se družim s tobom. (I am not free to hang out with you.)